'''江韶宗'''（{{bd|1453年||1504年||Jiang}}），字舜夫，[[順天府|順天]]人，[[明朝|明朝]][[弘治|弘治]]年间的官员<ref name="ebby">Ebrey, Patricia B & al. ''Pre-modern East Asia to 1800: A Cultural, Social, and Political History'' 3rd ed., [http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=BZ8WAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA239 p. 239] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=BZ8WAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA239 |date=20181106005045 }}. Cengage Learning, 2013. ISBN 1285546237. Accessed 7 Feb 2014.</ref>。

姜韶宗官居六品，其官服像，現藏[[南京博物院|南京博物院]]<ref name=guan>Guan Shanming. ''[http://books.google.com.hk/books?ei=t_j0UrT7AsuXiAeI9IFA Chinese Portraits] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com.hk/books?ei=t_j0UrT7AsuXiAeI9IFA |date=20140222152105 }}'', p. 33. Muwen Tang Fine Arts Publication Ltd., 2003.</ref>。

